1
00:01:12,440 --> 00:01:15,200
I sincerely swear

2
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:19,520
to volunteer to join the Nanyang Overseas Chinese Mechanics Returning Home Service Corps,

3
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,800
to obey work arrangements,

4
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,200
to abide by discipline,

5
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,520
to support the War of Resistance,

6
00:01:23,520 --> 00:01:24,960
to be loyal to the motherland,

7
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,360
to fulfill my duties,

8
00:01:26,360 --> 00:01:27,720
to not fear sacrifice,

9
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:31,640
and to swear to fight to the end for national liberation.

10
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,600
So I swear.

11
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,080
Grandma.

12
00:01:48,640 --> 00:01:49,440
Grandma,

13
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,240
I'm going back to our country.

14
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,160
Going back?

15
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:58,080
Yes, going back.

16
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,850
Going back to China.

17
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:03,520
What are you going to do in China?

18
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:10,199
To join the War of Resistance,

19
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:11,330
to save the country,

20
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,890
and to transport supplies.

21
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:18,200
You are just an ordinary person, and you want to save the country?

22
00:02:18,200 --> 00:02:19,320
Can you carry a gun?

23
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:20,520
Can you fight in a war?

24
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,280
Grandma,

25
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,810
I'm not going to carry a gun.

26
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:24,940
I'm going to transport war supplies.

27
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,400
The Yunnan-Burma Road in China has been built.

28
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:29,560
They urgently need mechanics who can drive and repair cars

29
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,690
to deliver supplies to the frontline.

30
00:02:31,960 --> 00:02:33,280
Can you drive

31
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:34,880
and repair cars?

32
00:02:36,160 --> 00:02:38,680
When I was working in the rubber plantation,

33
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,940
I learned it secretly.

34
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:47,360
No wonder your hands are covered in calluses.

35
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:52,520
Since ancient times,

36
00:02:52,520 --> 00:02:55,400
the Japanese pirates have always been disturbing us,

37
00:02:55,400 --> 00:02:57,920
making the residents along our coast

38
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,400
live in destitution.

39
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,680
Your grandpa and I

40
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,880
fled to Nanyang back then.

41
00:03:03,400 --> 00:03:06,200
After decades of hard work,

42
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:09,200
we finally have this moment of peace.

43
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,000
Your father passed away early.

44
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:15,080
You are my only grandson.

45
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:20,120
Do you really have to go back?

46
00:03:21,040 --> 00:03:22,280
Grandma,

47
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,740
now the Japanese pirates,

48
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,320
no,

49
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,800
the Japanese invaders.

50
00:03:27,720 --> 00:03:29,160
More than half of the Chinese land

51
00:03:29,160 --> 00:03:30,620
has been occupied by them.

52
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,460
They occupied our land

53
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,079
and killed our compatriots.

54
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,730
They are totally inhumane.

55
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:38,440
This bunch of robbers

56
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:39,770
are worse than robbers.

57
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,840
The numerous crimes they have committed

58
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:45,300
are simply infuriating to both men and gods.

59
00:03:48,120 --> 00:03:49,760
Grandma,

60
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,440
you taught me since I was a child

61
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:53,200
to be a responsible man.

62
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,360
Now that the country is in peril,

63
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,760
how can our home survive?

64
00:03:59,480 --> 00:04:02,240
It's not easy for us Chinese.

65
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:04,560
We have what we have today

66
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:06,400
all by relying on unity.

67
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,800
Yes, unity.

68
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,260
Twist together into a rope so it won't break.

69
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:14,600
Grandma,

70
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,399
I have already signed up

71
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,399
and passed the exam.

72
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,680
There's an exam?

73
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:19,600
Of course.

74
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,640
Those who can pass are not ordinary people.

75
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:24,100
Your grandson is considered one of the best.

76
00:04:25,160 --> 00:04:26,880
You have grown up.

77
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,480
I will take you to a place tomorrow,

78
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,240
okay?

79
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,960
It's God's will.

80
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,930
In the past few decades,

81
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:25,440
I pray to the heavens every day

82
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:28,080
to bless us with peace and safety.

83
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,640
In these troubled times,

84
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:33,340
you are going back to our country.

85
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:35,200
Ah Ma, my heart,

86
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:37,960
truly cannot let it go.

87
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,640
I can only ask

88
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:42,800
the gods to bless us,

89
00:05:42,800 --> 00:05:45,159
to bless Hanwen with peace and safety.

90
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:49,480
He is the only bloodline of the Chen family.

91
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:53,880
I beg the gods to keep him safe.

92
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,480
I beg the gods to bless Ah Ma

93
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,010
with health and longevity.

94
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,420
Wait for my return.

95
00:06:00,280 --> 00:06:01,520
I also pray that the war

96
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,560
will end soon,

97
00:06:02,960 --> 00:06:04,200
so that people all over the world

98
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:05,800
will no longer be displaced.

99
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,600
Ah Ma, slow down.

100
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:32,640
This lotus seed was dug up by our ancestors.

101
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:34,240
It has strong vitality

102
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,360
and can ward off disasters and misfortunes.

103
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:39,200
May it bless you with peace and safety.

104
00:06:39,200 --> 00:06:41,000
When you return to our country this time,

105
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,600
you must be honest in everything you do,

106
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,060
and have no evil thoughts.

107
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:47,240
Keep it with you to bless you with peace and safety.

108
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,760
Ah Ma will wait for you to come back.

109
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:51,640
Lotus seed,

110
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:53,520
connecting sons.

111
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,159
Ah Ma,

112
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,560
doesn't this lotus seed resemble us overseas wanderers,

113
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:58,090
connecting with our roots?

114
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,440
This lotus seed is also called 'connected hearts',

115
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:03,240
just as if our hearts are connected together.

116
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,000
Wearing it,

117
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:06,480
is like I am with Ah Ma.

118
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:12,200
Ah Ma, rest assured,

119
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,400
Hanwen will definitely

120
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,260
return safely.

121
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,880
Let's go.

122
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:40,440
Gods above,

123
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,200
returning to the country this time,

124
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,600
I do not know the dangers.

125
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,520
If I do not complete the mission,

126
00:07:47,600 --> 00:07:49,000
I will never return home.

127
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:52,280
I only ask you to bless Ah Ma

128
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,880
with good health and safety,

129
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:55,920
and that our home in Nanyang

130
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:57,720
will always have a full rice bin.

131
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:05,120
If I die in my motherland,

132
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,850
please send a dream to Ah Ma.

133
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,720
Just say,

134
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,840
her grandson

135
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:15,370
went to a Nanyang trading firm to learn business,

136
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:18,040
and won't return for eight or ten years.

137
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:14,320
Hanwen,

138
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,320
come have the New Year's Eve dinner.

139
00:09:16,760 --> 00:09:17,720
Hanwen.

140
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,640
Hanwen.

141
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,920
Hanwen.

142
00:09:45,880 --> 00:09:47,320
During the New Year,

143
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,380
with millions of homes lit up,

144
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:53,080
at least take a bite of the New Year's Eve dinner

145
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,080
before you go.

146
00:09:57,920 --> 00:09:59,360
Oh, heavens,

147
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:01,920
bless my Awen

148
00:10:01,920 --> 00:10:04,480
with a safe journey.

149
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,680
Why are you so slow?

150
00:10:18,680 --> 00:10:19,480
The suitcase.

151
00:11:01,440 --> 00:11:01,920
Ah Ma,

152
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,200
take care of your health.

153
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,320
Forgive Hanwen

154
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,370
for being unfilial.

155
00:11:23,520 --> 00:11:25,640
Ah Ma will wait for you to come back.

156
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,690
When the time comes,

157
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,240
when Ah Ma sees me return,

158
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,680
she will definitely tell everyone.

159
00:11:38,760 --> 00:11:40,440
My grandson

160
00:11:40,440 --> 00:11:41,560
is so promising.

161
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,680
He's returning to join the Resistance.

162
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:46,920
He's a real man now.

163
00:11:48,840 --> 00:11:49,840
I will.

164
00:12:23,440 --> 00:12:24,240
Grandpa,

165
00:12:24,920 --> 00:12:28,120
forgive me for leaving before finishing New Year's Eve dinner.

166
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,400
Loyalty and filial piety have always been hard to balance.

167
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:31,840
I am returning today

168
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,440
to save our country

169
00:12:34,080 --> 00:12:35,280
and protect our home.

170
00:12:36,600 --> 00:12:37,860
Don't worry, Grandpa.

171
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:39,680
I have a mission

172
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:42,080
and will remember our ancestors' teachings.

173
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:43,540
If anything happens to me,

174
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:45,930
please don't be sad.

175
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,600
Your unfilial grandson,

176
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:49,680
Yaozu.

177
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:51,400
My grandson!

178
00:12:52,680 --> 00:12:54,200
This is what a real man

179
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:55,640
should do.

180
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:08,120
By the way,

181
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:10,280
Yiyi watched time-travel shows all night yesterday

182
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:12,520
and said she's found a way to send you back.

183
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:13,320
Really?

184
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:14,680
Of course.

185
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:17,680
She didn't watch those shows for nothing.
